cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.DB

The paper discusses the development of an interpretable and interactive automated machine learning service, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions pipeline search and hyper-parameter tuning, which are common techniques in data science and data mining, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a likely sub-category as well. The service is also part of the Maana Knowledge Platform, which is a software engineering platform, making cs.SE (Software Engineering) a possible sub-category. Finally, the service generates structured knowledge about decisions for pipeline profiling and selection, which involves data management and organization, making cs.DB (Databases) a possible sub-category.
